<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Invalid or Expired Token</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f8ff;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .container {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      width: 400px;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .logo img {
        max-width: 100px;
        max-height: 80px;
        object-fit: contain;
    }
    .message {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .message h1 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin: 0;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .message p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="http://localhost:9090/images/abbott-logo.png" alt="Abbott Logo">
        <img src="http://localhost:9090/images/freestyle-logo.png" alt="Freestyle Libre Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="message">
      <h1>Invalid or Expired Token</h1>
      <p>The token you provided is either invalid or has expired.<br>
      Please request a new verification link or contact support for assistance.</p>
    </div>
    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn">Go to Homepage</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
